## Review Scope

Compodoc + Storybook 10.3.5 integration for an Nx Angular 21.x library (`ngx-smart-components`). The changes wire Compodoc JSON generation into the Storybook build so JSDoc descriptions appear on the Docs tab via autodocs.

## Changes Made (committed as wip: 0620e93)

1. `package.json` -- added `"@compodoc/compodoc": "1.2.1"` (exact) to devDependencies; was extraneous transitive.
2. `packages/ngx-smart-components/tsconfig.doc.json` (new) -- extends `./tsconfig.lib.json`, includes `src/**/*.ts`. Inherits the lib tsconfig's exclude of spec/test/stories files.
3. `packages/ngx-smart-components/project.json` -- both `storybook` and `build-storybook` targets: `"compodoc": true` + `"compodocArgs": ["-e", "json", "-d", "packages/ngx-smart-components", "-p", "packages/ngx-smart-components/tsconfig.doc.json"]`.
4. `packages/ngx-smart-components/.storybook/main.ts` -- `addons: ['@storybook/addon-docs']`.
